    dc:creator "Cardoso, Giovanna Monticelli; Bastos-Pereira, Rafaela; Ferreira, Rodrigo Lopes" ;
    dc:date "2022" ;
    dc:title "Two new troglobitic species of Iansaoniscus from Brazilian caves (Crustacea, Isopoda, Pudeoniscidae)" ;
    fabio:hasPart <http://dx.doi.org/10.3897/subtbiol.43.81308.figure1>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.3897/subtbiol.43.81308.figure2>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.3897/subtbiol.43.81308.figure3>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.3897/subtbiol.43.81308.figure4>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.3897/subtbiol.43.81308.figure9> ;
    a fabio:JournalArticle .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.3897/subtbiol.43.81308.figure1>
    dc:description "Figure 1. Iansaoniscus leilae sp. nov. A male holotype, lateral view. Female paratype B cephalon, frontal view C cephalon, dorsal view D pereonites 1 and 2, dorsal view, arrow indicating the noduli laterales E pereonite 1, ventral view F pereonites 2 and 3, ventral view G pleonite 5, telson and uropod, dorsal view H antennal flagellum I uropod. Scale bars: 1 mm (A); 500 μm (B-I)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/696181" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.3897/subtbiol.43.81308.figure2>
    dc:description "Figure 2. Iansaoniscus leilae sp. nov. Male holotype A telson and uropod, dorsal view B antennula C antenna D left mandible E right mandible F maxillula G maxilla H maxilliped. Scale bars: 0.2 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/696182" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.3897/subtbiol.43.81308.figure3>
    dc:description "Figure 3. Iansaoniscus leilae sp. nov. Male holotype A pereopod 1 B pereopod 7 C pleopod 1 D pleopod 2 E pleopod 3 exopod F pleopod 4 exopod G pleopod 5 exopod. Scale bars: 0.2 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/696183" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.3897/subtbiol.43.81308.figure4>
    dc:description "Figure 4. Iansaoniscus leilae sp. nov. habitat A Toca do Goncalo cave entrance B cave floor in the inner portion of the cave, where specimens were found C water table at the cave lower level D adult specimen inside the cave, frontal view E adult specimen inside the cave, lateral view F diesel pump installed inside the cave in the 70 ' s G electric pump installed inside the cave in 2010." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/696184" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.3897/subtbiol.43.81308.figure9>
    dc:description "Figure 9. Geographical distribution of Iansaoniscus species, with Brazilian biomes and the karst areas delimited in the state of Bahia." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/696189" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

